@startuml ble-pairing-flow
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title BLE pairing and rename flow, CubeInfo GATT Service

actor "Companion App\n(btleplug)" as app
participant "BLE Peripheral\n(ESP32-S3 / trouble-host)" as cube

== Device Discovery ==
cube -> app : Advertisement (16-bit UUID **0xCBFF**,\ndevice name "CubeMaster")
note right of cube
  Advertising PDU includes:
  · 16-bit service UUID 0xCBFF
  · Local name (user-configurable)
  · TX Power level
end note

app -> app : Filter scan results\nby service UUID 0xCBFF

== Connection ==
app -> cube : Connect
app -> cube : Negotiate MTU 247
app -> cube : Discover GATT Services

note right of cube
  **CubeInfo Service**
  UUID: c0bea577-0000-4000-8000-00000000f001

  Characteristics:
  ├─ cube_name  (UUID: ...f004) [Read+Write] [u8;32]
  ├─ status     (UUID: ...ffe2) [Read+Notify] u8
  ├─ wifi_ssid  (UUID: ...f011) [Write]       [u8;32]
  └─ wifi_pass  (UUID: ...f012) [Write]       [u8;32]
end note

== Rename Flow ==
app -> cube : Read cube_name → "CubeMaster"
app -> cube : Write cube_name ← "MyDnDCube" (UTF-8 bytes)
cube -> cube : Update advertising name\nin RAM

== WiFi Provisioning ==
app -> cube : Write wifi_ssid ← "HomeNetwork" (UTF-8 bytes)
app -> cube : Write wifi_pass ← "s3cr3t!" (UTF-8 bytes)
cube -> cube : Store credentials\n(RAM only, not yet NVS)

== Status Notification ==
cube --> app : status.Notify (connection state change)

== Disconnect & Re-advertise ==
app -> cube : Disconnect
cube -> cube : Resume advertising with\nnew name "MyDnDCube"

== Subsequent Discovery ==
cube -> app : Advertisement (UUID 0xCBFF,\nname "MyDnDCube")
note over app
  App recognizes the device
  by UUID 0xCBFF, not by name
end note

@enduml
